    <div class="card text-bg-primary mb-3" style="max-width: 18rem;">
      <div class="card-header">Feature 01</div> 
      <div class="card-body">
        <h5 class="card-title">Student Feedback Submission:</h5>
        <p class="card-text">Students are provided with a platform where they can easily share their opinions, suggestions, and concerns regarding different aspects of their academic journey. This might include feedback about courses, instructors, facilities, and overall campus experience.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card text-bg-secondary mb-3" style="max-width: 18rem;">
